        {
            "id": 6169308,
            "title": "台股重挫逾500點 高檔股搖搖欲墜 千金股18檔臉綠僅穎崴獨紅",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台股本周勢如破竹，一度達 26394 點歷史新高，但隨著教師節連假即將到來，高檔獲利了結賣壓出籠，影響今 (26) 日重挫超過 500 點，千金股也成為資金撤離的主要對象，19 檔千金股中僅穎崴 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6515:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6515\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6515-TW</a>) 維持上漲，其餘 18 檔全面走跌，也壓抑大盤走勢。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6169308/l/c753eb933ee27db71b00fc89e4c746f4.jpg\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">台股重挫超過500點 18千金股遭提款。(鉅亨網資料照)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>穎崴近日傳出好消息，再度拿下美系 AI 晶片大廠訂單，且最新一代測試座 Hyper socket 因針數顯著提升，單價也跟著大增，在客戶需求帶動下，明年將放量出貨，同時在系統級測試 (SLT) 的市佔率也節節攀升。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>股王信驊 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5274:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5274\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5274-TW</a>) 日前跟著台股走強，最高衝上 5405 元，但隨著資金在高檔調節，今日股價也下挫超過 2%，下跌超過 100 元，跌破季線大關；第二高價股世芯 - KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3661:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3661\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3661-TW</a>) 近來因外資、投信不斷減碼，股價持續弱勢，盤中下探至 3230 元，為三個月來新低。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>其他如川湖 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2059:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2059\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2059-TW</a>)、緯穎 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6669:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6669\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6669-TW</a>)、大立光 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3008:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3008\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3008-TW</a>)、健策 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3653:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3653\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3653-TW</a>)、精測 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6510:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6510\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6510-TW</a>)、旺矽 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6223:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6223\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6223-TW</a>)、嘉澤 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3533:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3533\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3533-TW</a>)、祥碩 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5269:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5269\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5269-TW</a>)、聯發科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2454:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2454\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2454-TW</a>)、創意 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3443:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3443\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3443-TW</a>)、台光電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2383:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2383\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2383-TW</a>)、印能科技 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:7734:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/7734\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">7734-TW</a>) 跌幅都在 1% 至 4% 間。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>力旺 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3529:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3529\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3529-TW</a>)、弘塑 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3131:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3131\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3131-TW</a>)、AES-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6781:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6781\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6781-TW</a>) 跌勢較重，下跌幅度至少 6% 起跳。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
